~ Monster_Disappear

%2 Boss: Lass mich nicht so lange warten!
do GlobalFunctions.DecreaseVisibilityOnMonsterIsland()
% Boss: HAHAHA!
do GlobalFunctions.IncreaseVisibilityOnMonsterIsland()
% Boss: HAHAHA!
do GlobalFunctions.PlayIdleOnMonsterIsland()
% Boss: Ich warte!
do GlobalFunctions.LeaveDialogue()

=> END

~ Monster_Appear

% Boss: The time is running!
% Boss: I'AM HUNGRY!
%2 Boss: Don't let me wait so long!
Boss: ROAW!
do GlobalFunctions.LeaveDialogue()

=> END